{"Title":"炝炒儿菜的做法","Primary":["娃娃菜儿菜300克"],"Auxiliary":["花生油20克","花椒粒10颗","干辣椒4个","食盐5克","葱1根"],"Flavoring":[],"Setups":["1.儿菜去皮切片，用食盐腌制五分钟","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/41/143/2723291/n2723291_142262062732090.jpg","2.干辣椒切段、花椒粒洗净、葱切成葱花备用","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/41/143/2723291/n2723291_142262070318732.jpg","3.油烧热，将花椒粒和干辣椒放入锅中爆香","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/41/143/2723291/n2723291_142262075906946.jpg","4.炒出香味后放入洗净的儿菜翻炒均匀","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/41/143/2723291/n2723291_142262076819967.jpg","5.儿菜出水变软后放入食盐","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/41/143/2723291/n2723291_142262081531220.jpg","6.撒上葱花，炒匀即可","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/41/143/2723291/n2723291_142262083400704.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/41/143/2723291/n2723291_142262089304719.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/41/143/2723291/n2723291_142262092159595.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/41/143/2723291/n2723291_142262092408090.jpg"]}